cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper deals with a machine learning algorithm (LSSVM) and proposes a new algorithm (SR-LSSVM) that overcomes two of its drawbacks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed algorithm is also tested on image classification problems (cs.CV). The use of low-rank matrix approximation and entropy penalty function also suggests the possibility of neural network applications (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with optimization and efficiency of the algorithm, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI).
